Golden State 's Stephen Curry scored 40 points , including a 3-pointer in the final seconds of regulation to complete a 20-point , fourth-quarter comeback that allowed the Golden State Warriors to beat New Orleans 123-119 in overtime Thursday and take 3-0 lead in their first-round play-off series .
The win by the Warriors was mirrored by Chicago 's double-overtime victory over Milwaukee .
Derrick Rose scored 34 points and Jimmy Butler in playoff series .